# Root .dockerignore — build context is the monorepo root.
# Keep the context small; Dockerfiles copy manifests + the one package they need.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.git
.git
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/data
**/web-output
**/exports
**/results
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.expo
**/*.log
.DS_Store
**/screenshots
**/.pnpm-store
